      <title>德勤：瑞信破产导致瑞士财富领先地位下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/credit-suisse-collapse-puts-switzerland-s-wealth-lead-at-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德勤的一份报告显示，瑞士信贷破产后，瑞士作为全球主要财富聚集地的地位岌岌可危。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/credit-suisse-collapse-puts-switzerland-s-wealth-lead-at-risk</guid>
